Encoding
--------


MPEG-2 encoder - libmpeg2:
mencoder videos/576p25_blue_sky.yuv -demuxer rawvideo -rawvideo fps=25:w=720:h=576 -o 576p25_blue_sky_mpeg2.avi -ofps 25 -ovc lavc -lavcopts vcodec=mpeg2video:vqscale=5:vmax_b_frames=2:subq=8:psnr


MPEG-4 encoder - libavcodec:
mencoder videos/576p25_blue_sky.yuv -demuxer rawvideo -rawvideo fps=25:w=720:h=576 -oac lavc -ovc lavc -lavcopts vcodec=mpeg4:vbitrate=700:acodec=ac3:abitrate=192 -srate 44100 -vf scale=320:240 -o 576p25_blue_sky.avi


MPEG-4 encoder - Xvid:
mencoder videos/576p25_blue_sky.yuv -demuxer rawvideo -rawvideo fps=25:format=i420:w=176:h=144 -o 576p25_blue_sky_mpeg4.avi -ofps 25 -ovc xvid -xvidencopts fixed_quant=5:max_bframes=2:qpel:psnr


x264 encoder:
mencoder -demuxer rawvideo -rawvideo fps=25:w=720:h=576 -ovc x264 -x264encopts qp=26:subq=5:8x8dct:frameref=2:bframes=3:b_pyramid=normal:weight_b:pass=1 -o null -nosound videos/576p25_blue_sky.yuv

mencoder -demuxer rawvideo -rawvideo fps=25:w=720:h=576 -ovc x264 -x264encopts qp=26:subq=5:8x8dct:frameref=2:bframes=3:b_pyramid=normal:weight_b:pass=2 -o 576p25_blue_sky_x264.avi -oac mp3lame -lameopts mode=3:vbr=3:br=128 videos/576p25_blue_sky.yuv

